Correct armaments. She never had an Exocet refit
Served in her until November 1982. Big noisy gun on the front, and a Wasp on the back.
She was never converted to Exocet, and today sits on the sea floor off Wellington with the original 4.5" turret gathering seaweed. Never had a Lynx either. Wasp "425"
